  #transitive triples = C(n,3) + 2*C(n,3) - 3*t₃ ?
  Actually: #tt = 3*C(n,3) - 3*t₃ = n(n-1)(n-2)/2 - 3*t₃
  (Each 3-set contributes either 3 transitive triples (if transitive) or 0 (if 3-cycle))
  Wait: a 3-set with a 3-cycle has 0 transitive triples. A transitive 3-set has 3.
  So #tt = 3*(C(n,3) - t₃)
